b34051315349fb09e7e5741e0a5516c1c5f83019332f7150b969c57d211b235b366cf19ba5e4929817202f721abbeb74359ada4d238aee843b963272983475cb  0001-incidenceeditor-Use-renamed-kdiagram.patch
3793a42b42db07bcacaff0642c0072efcc1ef6c9f32641ba196dcf0dfd1223a5752d11c18ddfce6de4a8770bfdf0b107be9dc6fe7da2dd44f79f7a1787c7b1c1  0002-incidenceeditor-Look-for-KF6TextWidgets-explicitly.patch
"
